</para>
<para id="element-83">Similarly, in a process known as “pair production”, energy is converted into a pair of positron and electron as :
</para>
<para id="element-84">
<m:math display="block">
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mi>h</m:mi>
    <m:mi>v</m:mi>
